HOW TO RUN:

rename and edit config file

Start hadcc with:
$ runhaskell Hadcc.hs


HOW TO INSTALL:

install missing libraries with "cabal install libx"

$ runhaskell Setup.lhs configure --prefix=$HOME --user
$ runhaskell Setup.lhs build
$ runhaskell Setup.lhs install

